original_title: The Dive Bar Tour: Lady Gaga Live in L.A.
overview: The Dive Bar Tour, sponsored by Bud Light, was a promotional tour by American singer Lady Gaga, in support of her fifth studio album Joanne (2016). The 3-date tour, which visited dive bars in the United States, had dates on October 5, 20 and 27.
